{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775838738553,"sessionID":"ses_287c41230ffeXbDTAqLInJPFKF","part":{"id":"prt_d783ca3f7001fXLKu9AHC5VhfY","messageID":"msg_d783c67570014DNs3ui59NXF0q","sessionID":"ses_287c41230ffeXbDTAqLInJPFKF","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-e18a6e0770cf47a38c8527a976e17b27","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/spec.md","content":"# AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n\n定义 AgentRuntime CRD 的 Go 类型结构，包括:\n- `AgentRuntime` 类型及其 `Spec`、`Status`\n- `AgentRuntimeList` 类型\n- `CodeInterpreter` 类型及其 `Spec`、`Status`\n- `CodeInterpreterList` 类型\n- 相关常量、标签、注解定义\n\n## Out of Scope\n\n- Controller 实现\n- Webhook 验证逻辑\n- CRD YAML 生成\n- client-go 代码生成\n\n## Dependencies\n\n无外部依赖。\n\n## Deliverables\n\n| File | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go` | AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter 类型定义 |\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go` | 包文档 |\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go` | Scheme 注册 |\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] 类型定义符合 Kubernetes API conventions\n- [ ] JSON tags 使用 camelCase\n- [ ] 包含完整的字段注释\n- [ ] 通过 `go vet` 和 `golangci-lint`\n\n## References\n\n- Kubernetes API Conventions: https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/spec.md","time":{"start":1775838738538,"end":1775838738551}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775838738556,"sessionID":"ses_287c41230ffeXbDTAqLInJPFKF","part":{"id":"prt_d783cb84e00174tcjE6hRXZ8f3","messageID":"msg_d783c67570014DNs3ui59NXF0q","sessionID":"ses_287c41230ffeXbDTAqLInJPFKF","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-8f184f6c100f4fa493c1f3c013b6f47f","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/design.md","content":"# AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n定义 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 的 Go 类型结构，作为 agentcube 的核心数据模型。\n\n## Design\n\n（待填写）\n\n## Data Structures\n\n（待填写）\n\n## API Schema\n\n（待填写）\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n（待填写）\n\n## File Structure\n\n```\npkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n  types.go      — AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n  doc.go        — 包文档\n  register.go   — Scheme 注册\n```\n\n## Open Questions\n\n- 是否需要定义默认值？\n- Status 字段的完整定义？"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/design.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/design.md","time":{"start":1775838738542,"end":1775838738554}}}}
